{"tid":759613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 對未來好絕望 好辛苦","createTime":"2018-07-28T18:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T14:49:01.000Z","uid":160405,"like":8,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e845833f87c68befee47ca50107a2c1dddaec979","tid":759613,"uid":160405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"講番少少背景<br />\n小弟三大fg 月入都有25k<br />\n有個拍咗拖三年嘅女朋友 感情都好穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺好多人眼中算幾叻仔<br />\n<br />\n不過真係有苦自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企係夾心階層 租緊樓 月月清<br />\n所以買樓方面唯有靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家每個月都叫儲到一萬蚊<br />\n但計過想買間好少少嘅黎組織家庭都要儲十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後再每個月用三份之一糧黎供到死嗰日<br />\n真係諗起都想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計結婚用嘅錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一唔小心有咗BB 真係含撚都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家莫講去下旅行 食好啲啲<br />\n晏晝嗌個凍飲都要思前想後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486e691fd2e1f7368bb4e1b5e13145e0214f6a79","tid":759613,"uid":160405,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T18:50:54.000Z","msg":"點解咁都要負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7786465a474803cbe5987511a745f036d365aa78","tid":759613,"uid":160405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"唔通真係冇人同我有差唔多經歷咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60396140284872aeed4559760b36ca8b2ad9ee7","tid":759613,"uid":160405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"圍堵取個暖又好 指點下都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1c5dd66c58afb95fe774be1a7933c6c280aaa0","tid":759613,"uid":7